China Power Is Willing to Buy 20% of EDP, Diario Economico Says

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-08-05T07:05:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/china-power-is-willing-to-buy-20-of-edp-diario-economico-says.html
China Power International is willing
to buy a 20 percent stake in utility EDP-Energias de Portugal SA
that the Portuguese government plans to sell, Diario Economico
reported, citing unidentified people linked to the process.  The Chinese company had initially considered buying a 10
percent stake in EDP, the Portuguese newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joao Lima at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net  